title: Most Asian markets rise as traders await key US data
description: Markets mostly rose Wednesday, following a resumption of Wall Street’s rally, but gains were muted as investors await the last tranche of US data before next week’s Federal Reserve meeting. With a third successive interest rate cut already priced in, trading …
content:
